snippet.title: Redemption's Guild Update #6! Areda Dunes
snippet.description:
Redemption's Guild is an online VR RPG for the HTC Vive and Oculus Rift.

In this video we walk through our 2nd open adventure zone map - Areda Dunes.

For more information check out our website https://www.unlitgames.com, be sure to subscribe to stay updated!
